decks.notes: The key concept of this deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a swarm of small, efficient white creatures. The deck focuses on exploiting the strength of low-cost creatures and leveraging their abilities to gain an advantage. It includes a variety of cards that provide protection, disruption, and removal to keep the opponent on their toes. The deck also incorporates equipment and enchantments to enhance the creature's power and survivability. It utilizes a mix of aggressive and defensive creatures, along with a range of disruptive spells to control the board. The strategy is to apply constant pressure and maintain board presence, slowly chipping away at the opponent's life total.
